            <p>I’m a junior full-stack software developer, based near Amsterdam. Originally from the UK, I moved to the Netherlands mid-2022 for career, social and family reasons. I have experience in founding companies (see CV link opposite for more details) and have recently transitioned into a career in software development.</p><br>
