            <p><b>Back-end : Ruby, Ruby on Rails + SQL</b></p>
            <p><b>Tools: GitHub, Gitflow, Figma + Heroku</b></p><br>
            <p>For more info, click on the CV/cover letter links opposite - or see the contact section below to discuss opportunities.</p>
